web.auth.passwordReset.emailSent.text: Kua tukuna he īmēra ki a koe me tētahi hononga hei tautuhi anō i te kupuhipa mō tō pūkete

web.auth.terms.agree_prefix.text: E whakaae ana au ki te

web.auth.account.not_verified.text: Kāore anō kia Manatokohia te Īmēra

web.auth.verify._guidance.context.text: Te rere manatoko īmēra i muri i te waitohu

web.help.magic_link_not_arriving.text: Kāore te hononga karakia e tae mai ana?

web.help.try_again.text: Whakamātauria te tono i tētahi hononga hou mēnā kua neke atu i te 10 meneti

web.help.use_magic_link_instead.text: Whakamahia te kōwhiringa Hononga Karakia hei takiuru me te kore kupuhipa. Kia takiuru ana, ka taea e koe te huri i tō kupuhipa i ngā Tautuhinga Pūkete.

web.help.account_locked.text: Kua rakaina te pūkete mō te wā poto?

web.help.account_locked_explanation.text: I muri i ngā nganatanga takiuru hē maha, ka rakaina ngā pūkete mō te wā poto hei tiaki. Tatari 15 meneti ka whakamātau anō, whakamahia rānei te Hononga Karakia hei takiuru.

web.help.contact_us_description.text: Mēnā kei te raru tonu koe, kei konei mātou hei āwhina. Tukuna mai he karere ka whakautu mātou i te wā tata.

web.login.secure_link_helper.text: Ka tukuna he hononga haumaru ki tō pouaka īmēra.
